This paper proposes a new algorithm for finding abstract MDPs in environments with continuous state spaces, which is a problem commonly addressed in the machine learning community. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning in the proposed algorithm, which suggests that it may fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with robotics and control problems, which could place it under the categories of cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the use of data structures and algorithms, which could place it under the category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
